        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks for sheets of new book. Intends to talk about it at a scientific social club meeting.</p>
            <p>Is amused to read CD’s criticisms of his own style, as in the U. S. it is spoken of as being as faultless as his temper. Corrects a reference.</p>
